name: Impex Marketing
overview:
Established in the year 1997, “Impex Marketing” has attained an unrivaled position in the global market. With wide expertise and in-depth knowledge in this realm, we manufacture and supply a world-class gamut of industrial ventilators including Turbine Air Ventilator, FRP Base Plate, FRP Sheet, Anti Corrosive FRP Chemical Equipment, FRP Pipe & Fitting, FRP Door and FRP Security Cabin.

Our Team: Our superlative production processes coupled with a highly trained and dedicated workforce enable us to manufacture a wide range of products according to the customer specifications while conforming to the international quality and safety standards.

Our Quality: Being a quality conscious manufacturing entity, we undertake varied stringent measures in order to achieve highest industrial standards in our range. Moreover, we have employed a team of quality controllers who possess years of experience in this domain.

Our Infrastructure: Well integrated with a sturdy infrastructural unit, we are able to provide a wide range of products within the given time frame. Our infrastructure incorporates advanced design, fabrication, packaging, storage, and allied facilities that give us a competitive edge in meeting the clients’ requirement.

Our Products: Turbine Air Ventilator Line FRP Base Plate Line FRP Sheet Line Anti Corrosive FRP Chemical Equipment Line FRP Gratings Line FRP Door
